{"name":"Rider's Bond","type":"technique","img":"/systems/tyoa/assets/default/art.png","system":{"lvl":"5","pattern":"white","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"description":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81ba63f1-7fff-428f-bb0a-40fb9754aaab\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(Animals 5): </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #741b47; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Requires a mountable companion.</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Your companion knows your weight on its back as well as you know its mass under you. You and your mount gain the following benefits:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">When using Trample, your target&rsquo;s Athletics skill check has a difficulty of 10.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-d