{"name":"Pack Leader","type":"technique","img":"/systems/tyoa/assets/default/art.png","system":{"lvl":"5","pattern":"white","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"description":"<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81ba63f1-7fff-428f-bb0a-40fb9754aaab\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"></span></p>\n<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-59a63401-7fff-347e-0f31-b34b1545f5f0\" dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(Animals 5): </span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #1155cc; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Requires Animal Companion</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Your skill with training and handling the animals under your care has allowed you to control multiple animals at once. You gain the ability to control a second animal companion. Additionally, your companions gain the following benefits:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12pt; font-family: Ubuntu,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: n